  "description": "A vibrant spring scene featuring a tree in full bloom, covered in delicate white flowers. The tree is centrally positioned, with its branches stretching outwards and downwards, creating a cascading effect of blossoms. Below the tree, a lush green lawn slopes gently downwards towards a paved road. Dense green foliage and other trees form a backdrop, creating a natural, woodland setting. A weathered tree stump sits near the base of the blooming tree, adding a touch of rustic charm. The overall impression is one of natural beauty and renewal.",
